{
  "id": "RAW_5cda08",
  "title": "一文详解：DeepSeek 第三天开源的 DeepGEMM",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/_XCr7gVxRGos6JhlFSuZ6g",
  "date": "2025-02-26 02:36:43",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:hsl(var(--border));text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">它来了，我们的源神 DeepSeek 它又来了</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b50b4aac-2cb6-48fd-0f47-da4ab444ea00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7222222222222222\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"900\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100014071\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b50b4aac-2cb6-48fd-0f47-da4ab444ea00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek 开源周的第三天，带来了</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">专为 Hopper 架构 GPU 优化的矩阵乘法库 — DeepGEMM</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这一库支持标准矩阵计算和混合专家模型（MoE）计算，为 DeepSeek-V3/R1 的训练和推理提供强大支持，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Hopper GPU 上达到 1350+FP8 TFLOPS 的高性能</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 的设计理念是简洁高效，核心代码仅约 300 行</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，同时在大多数矩阵尺寸下性能优于现有解决方案。该库支持三种数据排列方式：标准排列和两种专为混合专家模型设计的特殊排列（连续排列和掩码排列）。DeepGEMM 采用即时编译技术，不需要在安装时进行编译，代码结构清晰易懂，非常适合学习 GPU 优化技术。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">性能表现</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 在各种计算场景下表现出色。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;对于标准矩阵乘法，与基于 CUTLASS 3.6 的优化实现相比，速度提升 1.0 到 2.7 倍不等。小批量数据处理（M=64 或 128）获得了最显著的加速，最高达到 2.7 倍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">对于混合专家模型的计算，DeepGEMM 提供的两种特殊数据排列方式也有明显优势。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;连续排列方式适用于训练和批量推理阶段，速度提升约 1.1 到 1.2 倍；掩码排列方式专为实时推理设计，支持与 CUDA 图技术配合使用，同样能提速 1.1 到 1.2 倍。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">考虑到官方的数据不太易读，</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\">我给重新做了 3 张，请叫我赛博菩萨</span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f3459f0e-9628-4ac8-dd1b-4e4c5b385b00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.7777777777777777\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:100%;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"1028\" data-imgfileid=\"100014082\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/f3459f0e-9628-4ac8-dd1b-4e4c5b385b00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8784c750-4e26-45c6-53a2-15392520eb00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.9425925925925925\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100014083\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8784c750-4e26-45c6-53a2-15392520eb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9bc256ea-4919-478a-ac39-4230e7f6f300/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.0472222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100014084\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9bc256ea-4919-478a-ac39-4230e7f6f300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">什么是 FP8 和 GEMM？</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在计算机中，数值需要用二进制位存储，存储方式决定了精度和所需空间。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">传统上，AI 计算使用 32 位浮点数（FP32），这提供了很高的精度，但占用较多存储空间和计算资源。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">研究表明，很多 AI 任务实际上不需要这么高的精度。16 位浮点数（FP16）已被广泛采用，而 8 位浮点数（FP8）是更进一步的精度降低。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然 FP8 精度较低，但对许多 AI 任务已经足够，同时能大大减少内存使用并提高计算速度。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;这就像用较粗的刻度测量大物体，虽然精度降低，但速度快得多，且在大多数情况下已经足够准确。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">GEMM（通用矩阵乘法）是深度学习中最基础也最常见的计算操作。简单来说，它计算两个数据表格（矩阵）相乘的结果。这看似简单，但在 AI 计算中，这些矩阵可能非常庞大，含有数百万个元素，使得矩阵乘法成为整个系统中最耗时的部分之一。几乎所有神经网络层的计算本质上都包含矩阵乘法操作。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 专门优化了 FP8 精度的矩阵乘法，同时解决了 Hopper 架构在处理 FP8 计算时可能出现的精度问题</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，确保计算结果准确可靠。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">标准矩阵乘法与混合专家模型计算</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">标准矩阵乘法处理的是完整矩阵之间的运算，适用于传统神经网络架构，所有数据都经过统一处理。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">而混合专家模型（MoE）是一种特殊的神经网络架构，它包含多个\"专家\"网络和一个\"门控\"网络。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;门控网络负责决定将输入数据分配给哪些专家处理，而不是所有数据都经过所有专家。这种方法允许模型规模大幅增长，同时保持计算效率，因为每次处理只激活部分模型而非全部。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对 MoE 模型，DeepGEMM 提供了两种特殊数据排列方式：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 连续排列：适用于训练和批量推理，将不同专家处理的数据连接成单一数据块</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 掩码排列：适用于实时推理，通过标记指示哪些数据需要处理，特别适合与 CUDA 图技术结合使用</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hopper GPU 与张量核心</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">NVIDIA 的 Hopper GPU 是专为人工智能和高性能计算设计的最新硬件平台，提供了多项关键技术改进：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">张量核心是 GPU 内部的特殊计算单元，专门针对矩阵运算进行了优化，能大幅加速深度学习计算。Hopper 架构的张量核心支持 FP8 计算，比前代产品提供更高性能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">TMA（张量内存加速器）是 Hopper 架构引入的新功能，用于更快速、异步地移动数据。DeepGEMM 充分利用 TMA 技术加载和存储数据，并使用 TMA 多播和描述符预取等高级功能进一步提升性能。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">即时编译技术</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">即时编译（Just-In-Time）是一种程序在运行时才进行编译的技术，而非传统的在安装或部署时预先编译。DeepGEMM 采用完全即时编译设计，所有计算内核都在实际运行时进行编译，这带来几个优势：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 可以将矩阵形状、块大小等作为编译时常量处理，从而节省计算资源并允许更多编译优化</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 自动为当前任务选择最佳参数配置，而无需人工调整</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 完全展开计算流水线，让编译器有更多优化空间，特别有利于处理小规模矩阵</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种即时编译方法显著提高了小矩阵形状的计算性能，技术思路类似于 Triton 等现代编译器。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">CUDA 与 CUTLASS</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">CUDA 是 NVIDIA 开发的并行计算平台和编程模型，允许开发者利用 GPU 强大的并行处理能力。这是编写 GPU 程序的基础工具。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">CUTLASS 是 NVIDIA 的开源矩阵乘法库，提供了高性能的矩阵计算模板。DeepGEMM 借鉴了 CUTLASS 的一些思路，但没有直接依赖其复杂的模板系统，而是自行实现了一套更简洁的代码，既保证性能又易于理解和学习。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">线程专业化技术</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 采用了线程专业化技术，这是一种高效的任务分工方法。在这种设计中，不同的计算线程被分配专门负责特定任务：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">一些负责数据移动，一些负责核心计算，一些负责结果处理。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">这种分工使得数据移动、计算和后处理能够同时进行，形成高效的流水线，大大提高整体性能。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/07bf701f-a2cc-4e85-047e-ddd6112cbf00/public\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3111111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100014081\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/07bf701f-a2cc-4e85-047e-ddd6112cbf00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术创新点</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 包含多项先进技术创新：</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 144, 169);font-size: 16.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.2;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">非标准块大小</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">传统上，GPU 计算通常使用标准大小的数据块（如 128×128）。</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 支持非标准块大小（如 112×128）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，这能更好地适应特定矩阵形状，提高硬件资源利用率。例如，对于 M=256，N=7168 的矩阵，标准块大小只能利用 112 个计算单元，而使用非标准块大小可以利用 128 个，效率提升明显。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 144, 169);font-size: 16.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.2;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">指令级优化</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过分析不同编译器版本产生的机器代码，DeepGEMM 团队发现并实现了特殊的指令排序优化。这种底层优化</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">调整了计算指令的执行方式，使计算单元能更高效地并行工作，显著提升了 FP8 计算性能。</span></strong></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 144, 169);font-size: 16.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.2;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">统一调度系统</span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 设计了一套统一的计算任务调度系统</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，采用特殊的排布策略，增强缓存重用效率，减少内存访问，提高整体性能。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用 DeepGEMM 需要支持 sm_90a 的 Hopper 架构 GPU、Python 3.8 以上、CUDA 12.3 以上（推荐 12.8 以上获得最佳性能）、PyTorch 2.1 以上以及 CUTLASS 3.6 以上。</span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 144, 169);font-size: 16.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.2;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Development</span></h3>\n  <pre style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:14px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:8px;font-feature-settings:normal;overflow-x:auto;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-family: Menlo, &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-size: 15px;display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;margin: 0px;white-space: nowrap;\"><span style=\"border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Submodule must be cloned</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">git&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;\"><span leaf=\"\">clone</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;--recursive git@github.com:deepseek-ai/DeepGEMM.git</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Make symbolic links for third-party (CUTLASS and CuTe) include directories</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">python setup.py develop</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Test JIT compilation</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">python tests/test_jit.py</span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span style=\"border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;\"><span leaf=\"\"># Test all GEMM implements (normal, contiguous-grouped and masked-grouped)</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><br></span><span leaf=\"\">python tests/test_core.py</span></code></pre>\n  <h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 3px;border-style: solid;border-left-color: rgb(0, 144, 169);font-size: 16.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 2em 8px 0.75em 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.2;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;padding-left: 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\"><span leaf=\"\">Installation</span></h3>\n  <pre style=\"padding:0px !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:14px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.5;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:8px;font-feature-settings:normal;overflow-x:auto;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-family: Menlo, &quot;Operator Mono&quot;, Consolas, Monaco, monospace;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-size: 15px;display: -webkit-box;padding: 0.5em 1em 1em;overflow-x: auto;text-indent: 0px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;margin: 0px;white-space: nowrap;\"><span leaf=\"\">python setup.py install</span></code></pre>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后, import&nbsp;</span><code style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-feature-settings: normal;font-variation-settings: normal;font-size: 13.5px;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(221, 17, 68);background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">deep_gemm</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;就行了</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 提供了清晰的 Python 编程接口，包括：</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));list-style: circle;margin: 0px;padding: 0px 0px 0px 1em;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 标准矩阵乘法函数：用于普通神经网络计算</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 连续排列分组函数：用于混合专家模型训练和批量推理</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;text-indent: -1em;display: block;margin: 0.2em 8px;color: rgb(63, 63, 63);\">\n    <section>\n     <span leaf=\"\">• 掩码排列分组函数：用于混合专家模型实时推理</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，库提供多个实用工具函数，用于设置计算资源和数据格式，让开发者能根据具体需求进行配置。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">回顾与展望</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">DeepGEMM 作为 DeepSeek 开源周的第三日发布，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">为 Hopper 架构 GPU 提供了高效的 FP8 矩阵乘法实现。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;通过精心设计的 300 行核心代码，这个库在多种场景下超越了现有解决方案，为普通神经网络和混合专家模型提供了强大的计算基础。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">同时，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\"><span leaf=\"\">其清晰的代码，也堪称是学习 GPU 优化技术的优质资源。</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">目前，DeepGEMM 专门针对 Hopper 架构 GPU 优化，未来可能扩展到更多硬件平台。</span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"padding:0px 0.2em;margin:4em auto 2em;font-weight:bold;display:table;font-size:18px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgb(0, 144, 169);border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后</span></h2>\n  <p style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:hsl(var(--border));line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: hsl(var(--border));font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(0, 144, 169);\">DeepSeek，源神，启动*3！</span></p>\n  <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:start;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;margin:0px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:hsl(var(--border));text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:0;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "DeepSeek 开源的 DeepGEMM 是专为 Hopper 架构 GPU 优化的矩阵乘法库，核心代码仅 300 行，性能超越现有方案，尤其在 FP8 计算和混合专家模型中表现出色，代码易于学习。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "DeepSeek 开源的 DeepGEMM 是专为 Hopper 架构 GPU 优化的矩阵乘法库，核心代码仅 300 行，性能超越现有方案，尤其在 FP8 计算和混合专家模型中表现出色，代码易于学习。",
  "summary": "DeepSeek 开源的 DeepGEMM 是一个专为 NVIDIA Hopper 架构 GPU 设计的矩阵乘法库，支持标准矩阵乘法和混合专家模型 (MoE) 计算。该库以简洁高效为设计理念，核心代码仅约 300 行，但在多种计算场景下性能优于现有解决方案，尤其在 FP8 精度计算和 MoE 模型中表现突出。DeepGEMM 提供了连续排列和掩码排列两种特殊数据排列方式，优化了 MoE 模型的训练和推理。此外，DeepGEMM 采用即时编译技术，无需预先编译，并充分利用 Hopper GPU 的张量核心和 TMA 技术，实现了指令级优化和统一调度系统，提高了缓存重用效率和整体性能。该库代码结构清晰易懂，适合学习 GPU 优化技术，易于学习和借鉴。",
  "mainPoints": [
